---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/CtaBand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Insights & Resources | Canyon Strategic Wealth"
  description="Practical guidance on investing, tax strategy, estate planning, and business-owner planning from Canyon Strategic Wealth."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Insights &amp; Resources</h1>
    <p>Practical guidance to help you make informed decisions about your financial future.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="section" aria-label="Financial Resources and Articles">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div class="section-eyebrow dark">Knowledge Center</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Latest Insights</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="resources-grid">
      <div class="resource-card fade-in">
        <div class="resource-card-img sky-bg">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card-body">
          <div class="resource-category">Investment Strategy</div>
          <h3>Understanding Market Volatility: A Long-Term Perspective</h3>
          <p>How disciplined investors weather market storms and why time in the market consistently outperforms timing the market.</p>
          <a class="resource-link" href="https://calendly.com/jakecazier/discovery-meeting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discuss with Us <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-left:4px"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="resource-card fade-in">
        <div class="resource-card-img navy-bg" style="color:var(--gold);">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M14.5 9.5c-.5-1-1.5-1.5-2.5-1.5-1.66 0-3 1-3 2.5S10.34 13 12 13c1.66 0 3 1 3 2.5S13.66 18 12 18c-1 0-2-.5-2.5-1.5"/><path d="M12 6v2"/><path d="M12 16v2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card-body">
          <div class="resource-category">Tax Planning</div>
          <h3>Roth Conversion Strategies: Is Now the Right Time?</h3>
          <p>Key factors to evaluate when considering a Roth conversion, including tax bracket analysis, time horizon, and estate planning implications.</p>
          <a class="resource-link" href="https://calendly.com/jakecazier/discovery-meeting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discuss with Us <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-left:4px"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="resource-card fade-in">
        <div class="resource-card-img gold-bg">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card-body">
          <div class="resource-category">Estate Planning</div>
          <h3>5 Estate Planning Mistakes High-Net-Worth Families Make</h3>
          <p>Common oversights that can cost your heirs significantly — and how proactive coordination with your attorney prevents them.</p>
          <a class="resource-link" href="https://calendly.com/jakecazier/discovery-meeting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discuss with Us <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-left:4px"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="resource-card fade-in">
        <div class="resource-card-img sky-bg">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card-body">
          <div class="resource-category">Risk Management</div>
          <h3>Beyond the Basics: Insurance Gaps Most Families Don't Know About</h3>
          <p>An umbrella policy isn't enough. Learn about the coverage gaps that leave high-net-worth families unexpectedly exposed.</p>
          <a class="resource-link" href="https://calendly.com/jakecazier/discovery-meeting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discuss with Us <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-left:4px"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="resource-card fade-in">
        <div class="resource-card-img navy-bg" style="color:var(--sky);">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2"/><line x1="2" y1="13" x2="22" y2="13"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card-body">
          <div class="resource-category">Business Owners</div>
          <h3>Exit Planning: Preparing Your Business for a Successful Transition</h3>
          <p>Whether you're planning to sell, transition to family, or bring in partners — the preparation starts years before the event.</p>
          <a class="resource-link" href="https://calendly.com/jakecazier/discovery-meeting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discuss with Us <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-left:4px"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="resource-card fade-in">
        <div class="resource-card-img gold-bg">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h2"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1" ry="1"/><line x1="8" y1="10" x2="16" y2="10"/><line x1="8" y1="14" x2="16" y2="14"/><line x1="8" y1="18" x2="12" y2="18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card-body">
          <div class="resource-category">Financial Planning</div>
          <h3>The Virtual Family Office: Why Coordination Matters More Than Returns</h3>
          <p>How an integrated approach to financial planning delivers better outcomes than managing each area in isolation.</p>
          <a class="resource-link" href="https://calendly.com/jakecazier/discovery-meeting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discuss with Us <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-left:4px"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    heading="Have a Question About Your Situation?"
    text="Schedule a complimentary discovery call and let's talk through what matters most to your family."
    ctaLabel="Schedule a Discovery Call"
  />
</BaseLayout>
